{"tid":997723,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"雙手佈滿怪疣就像「長出樹枝」　孟加拉「樹人」術後病情再惡化","createTime":"2019-01-27T11:41:06.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-27T12:16:41.000Z","uid":212399,"like":0,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"e659b68aa02d7d2bd78b43004d40de643debe609","tid":997723,"uid":212399,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-27T11:41:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/3866/d3866209.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F3866%2Fd3866209.jpg&h=6d5083d5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲孟加拉男子患罕見疾病，雙手肉疣如樹枝。（圖／新華社）<br />\n國際中心／綜合報導<br />\n孟加拉一名男子身染怪病，全身長滿樹皮般的肉疣，被大家稱作「樹人」，自2016年以來，他已經進行了超過25次手術，原本可望成為第1個治癒「樹人症」的成功案例。不過他卻沒有定期回診，導致病情再度惡化，現在「樹皮」範圍已擴散到全身，需再開刀5至6次，才有可能控制病情。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/3866/d3866224.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F3866%2Fd3866224.jpg&h=d8a3be82&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲巴強達手術前。（圖／翻攝自SBS NITV）<br />\n來自孟加拉國南部小鎮28歲的巴強達（Abul Bajandar），罹患因由免疫系統缺陷引起的「疣狀表皮發育不全」症（epidermodysplasia verruciformis），全球只有4起病例，患者皮膚會長出如樹皮般的肉疣，醫界稱之為「樹人症」。從10歲發病以來，巴強達無法自行吃飯，喝水，刷牙或洗澡。<br />\n2016年以來他已經進行超過25次手術，切除約11磅（約5公斤）的肉疣，原本病情一度穩定，但去年5月起巴強達卻沒有再回診。達卡醫院燒傷與整形外科醫生申恩（Samanta Lal Sen）表示，巴強達的病情相當複雜，我們多次要求回診，但他卻不肯，「20日巴強達回到醫院時，已經太遲，病情又再度惡化，這些肉疣甚至擴散到身體其他部位，必須要再重新擬定治療計畫。」<br />\n▼巴強達手術後一度好轉。（圖／翻攝自SBS NITV）<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/3866/d3866223.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F3866%2Fd3866223.jpg&h=d266b79b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/s_7mtA2v7IM\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fs_7mtA2v7IM&d=6cLUeJot05wT1KwRYHvTdqWGW%2FHqnCni%2B1xW1zXhD2s%3D&h=07bf56c4\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/s_7mtA2v7IM</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.ettoday.net/news/20190127/1367055.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ettoday.net%2Fnews%2F20190127%2F1367055.htm&d=6cLUeJot05wT1KwRYHvTdqWGW%2FHqnCni%2B1xW1zXhD2s%3D&h=aca15bee\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.ettoday.net/news/20190127/1367055.htm</a>"},{"pid":"1901797e99a0aa031f22053c145a2c3ba877653c","tid":997723,"uid":212399,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-27T11:42:12.000Z","msg":"I am groot"},{"pid":"2a62408888e7f664a42a10234ad1921afabfc25a","tid":997723,"uid":44323,"like":21,"dislike":1,"score":20,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-27T11:43:16.000Z","msg":"咪撚救呢D垃圾啦 又唔撚返去覆診"},{"pid":"6e99d5abc98c1b8e188c620e9cf9f8db80e9eab5","tid":997723,"uid":177089,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-27T11:44:17.000Z","msg":"不過他卻沒有定期回診，導致病情再度惡化<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n快啲死啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"99c674b2fa1bbd64e9d781deffdd32b2281f243e","tid":997723,"uid":82816,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-27T11:46:01.000Z","msg":"救返佢 等佢D genes傳出去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e10050644844173e9c289a44d60b65c230b8de34","tid":997723,"uid":23635,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-27T11:46:10.000Z","msg":"屌那星，又係呢啲核突野就有圖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"415c875bab76eb97fbde8be69099581a963cb1e4","tid":997723,"uid":35317,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-27T11:51:02.000Z","msg":"木遁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6724a7f0080b8f573a03e92d02ca42f1c5b1153b","tid":997723,"uid":16783,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-27T11:53:02.000Z","msg":"i am groot"},{"pid":"0d8d29fad757ee33dfb322d4e5816101f1a46887","tid":997723,"uid":207254,"like":0,"dislike":0,"sc